nodes.text: This female green-skinned Twi'lek was Jabba Desilijic Tiure's slave dancer before Nima'tar and Oola. During a performance for Jabba, he started pulling on her chain, dragging her towards him; she struggled with her end of the leash in protest. Jabba, angered by her defiance, triggered the trapdoor beneath her. She dropped into the rancor pit below where she was eaten alive by the crime lord's pet.
